ovider.getVerifyDockerfileSection()` generates:\n- `python3-pip python3-venv` (pip + venv)\n- `pip install ... coverage pytest` (verification tooling)\n- Semgrep in common layer\n\n```\noutput: Test \"PythonProvider.getVerifyDockerfileSection includes python3-pip\" passes\noutput: Test \"PythonProvider.getVerifyDockerfileSection includes python3-venv\" passes\n```\n\n## AC 5: Rust without Bevy — toolchain present, Bevy libs absent\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:** `src/lib/stacks/rust.ts:211-221` — Bevy libs only added when `hasCargoDep(depsSection, 'bevy')` is true.\n\n```\noutput: Test \"does NOT include Bevy system libs when bevy is not in Cargo.toml\" passes\noutput: Test \"includes Rust toolchain without Bevy\" passes\n```\n\n## AC 6: StackProvider interface has getVerifyDockerfileSection, all providers implement, TypeScript compiles\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `src/lib/stacks/types.ts:98`: `getVerifyDockerfileSection(projectDir: string): string;`\n- `src/lib/stacks/nodejs.ts:328`: implements method\n- `src/lib/stacks/python.ts:242`: implements method\n- `src/lib/stacks/rust.ts:200`: implements method\n- `npm run build`: TypeScript compilation succeeds with zero errors\n\n```\noutput: grep -c 'getVerifyDockerfileSection' src/lib/stacks/types.ts → 1\noutput: npm run build → Build success (0 errors)\n```\n\n## AC 7: Multi-stack project — Dockerfile includes tooling for ALL detected stacks\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:** `src/modules/verify/dockerfile-generator.ts:41-48` — iterates all detections from `detectStacks()` and calls each provider's `getVerifyDockerfileSection()`.\n\n```\noutput: Test \"multi-stack project generates sections for all stacks\" passes in dockerfile-generator.test.ts\n```\n\n## AC 8: npm run build succeeds with zero errors\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n```\noutput: npm run build → ESM ⚡️ Build success in 43ms, DTS ⚡️ Build success in 1503ms\n```\n\n## AC 9: npm test — all tests pass with zero regressions\n\n**Verdict:** PAS